  <brief_title>Intravenous Lidocaine in the Prevention of Postoperative Vomiting in Elective Tonsil Surgery</brief_title>
  <acronym>LETSVN</acronym>
  <official_title>Use of Intravenous Lidocaine in the Prevention of Postoperative Vomiting in Elective Tonsil Surgery, With or Without Adenoids</official_title>
  <sponsors>
