  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      There some evidence regarding the effect of lidocaine for the prevention of nausea and
      vomiting in adults.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators want to know whether with intravenous lidocaine a adjunct for general
      anesthesia for children between 2 and 12 years who are undergoing tonsillectomy, with or
      without adenoids has the same effect.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
